		<RichText x="739" y="223" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼岩龙蜥使用双爪划击，造成<span color="#ffe599">55.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼岩龙蜥在原地不断旋转，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">44.4%</span><span>伤害，旋转结束后施放强力尾刀，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼岩龙蜥蜷缩身子，朝玩家冲过来，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">83.3%</span><span>伤害，若命中玩家则立即弹开坠落，坠落造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害。若命中玩家身上的护盾，则会造成一段时间的眩晕。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，幼岩龙蜥会直接高空跳跃过来，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">83.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
