			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#937122">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/幼岩龙蜥.assets/Image_17.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/幼岩龙蜥.assets/Image_18.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1412" y="223" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼岩龙蜥蜷缩身子，在场地内无目的性的滚动，触碰持续造成<span color="#ffe599">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较远时，幼岩龙蜥钻地接近玩家，在钻入处掉落<span color="#ffdc72">2个岩结晶片</span><span>，该结晶盾可与其他结晶盾叠加，目前岩结晶盾仅能由此方法产生，其盾量取决于拾取的角色等级。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
